txt.en: Dolenthol asked you to travel to the second barricade and destroy it.
Shaktur is the leader of Ugrukhôr's forces, and seek the creature out and defeat it.
Dargásh is the leader of Gothmog's forces, and seek the creature out and defeat it.
You should seek out Shaktur, the leader of Ugrukhôr's forces, and defeat him.
You should seek out Dargásh, the leader of Gothmog's forces, and defeat him.

'Our actions have instigated a fight between Ugrukhôr's forces and those loyal to Gothmog! If fortune is on our side, this may allow the Rangers to proceed further into Minas Morgul.\n\n'But we should do what we can to better their chances of survival, and I know just the thing to do it: defeating the commanders of each army will throw the Orcs into disarray! To reach them we will need to clear several of the barricades between us and them, so let us begin.'
The Harrowing of Morgul is underway, and two Orc-armies do battle, each intent on seizing control of the Circle of Wrath for their master.
Dolenthol asked you to travel to the first barricade and destroy it.

TBD -  Our actions in the Circle of Wrath have led the forces allied to Ugrukhôr assaulting Gothmog's forces.   This engagement should allow the Rangers to progress further into Minas Morgul.  

If we were able to defeat the commanders of both Gothmog and Ugrukhôr's forces,  the orcs would pose a much less grave threat to the Ittilian position. 

First we must clear several barricades that have constructed between us and the commanders of the forces.
